    <p itemprop="text">
      Weekend conventions for Minnesota’s major political parties won’t head off primaries that could prove expensive and fierce for both the DFL and the GOP.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/06/01/dfl-gop-still-have-internal-divides-to-resolve-as-primaries-loom-in-governor-senate-races/"  >(Dana Ferguson and Peter Cox, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 01 Jun 2026 20:58:50 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 01 Jun 2026 20:58:50 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Jocelyn Noveck, Associated Press, Local 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static14/politics/2026/06/01/report-scott-pelley-of-60-minutes-accuses-cbs-news-head-bari-weiss-of-murdering-the-show.webp" alt="Scott Pelley of '60 Minutes' accuses CBS News head Bari Weiss of 'murdering' the show, report says" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Scott Pelley of '60 Minutes' accuses CBS News head Bari Weiss of 'murdering' the show, report says</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Reports say Scott Pelley has accused CBS head Bari Weiss of "murdering" the hugely successful “60 Minutes.”.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/06/01/report-scott-pelley-of-60-minutes-accuses-cbs-news-head-bari-weiss-of-murdering-the-show/"  >(Jocelyn Noveck, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div></div></fieldset></main>
